<br>
When the epics were first put in, a ton of clerics were stuck on Ragefire on E'ci, since there were plentiful public King and BW raids... we were often able to get 10 or so clerics their elementals done each evening every week or so, and regular king raids.  So the number of people that got their epics before the logjam, at least on our server, was pretty minimal.<br>
<br>
As for spawn numbers, all I can do is report what I see.  While Ragefire could spawn 24 hours or so after Naggy, he often wouldn't respawn until 3 to 4 days after that kill, so there was rarely a third Ragefire before Naggy spawned and started the timer over again.  It basically came down to 2 Rages per week, I've helped out on a number of camps and the average camp was 3-4 days each time.  Often getting 4 each week?  Man, you must have some weird mob timers on your server...<br>
<br>
